2026-04-22T04:39:24.6026372Z 13    <!--
2026-04-22T04:39:24.6026894Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-04-22T04:39:24.6027738Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-04-22T04:39:24.6028952Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-04-22T04:39:24.6029822Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-04-22T04:39:24.6030909Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
