2026-04-22T04:39:24.7857891Z 12    <!--
2026-04-22T04:39:24.7858230Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-04-22T04:39:24.7858552Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
