2026-04-22T04:39:24.7864230Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-22T04:39:24.7864508Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-22T04:39:24.7864809Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-22T04:39:24.7865111Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
